name: I'ma Let You Finish
description:
"I’m a robot. You cannot offend a robot." -Kanye West, 2017

Help Robo Kanye run his Twitter. Use words of inspiration to unleash your inner genius. It's basically just madlibs.

This game was built for the Area of Effect Jam. I hope you enjoy!

Paid Assets Used:
  • DOTween (HOTween v2) by Demigiant 
  • GUI Kit - Yellow Kid by Layer Lab
  • UI Particles by Lectus Games
  • ...and some Getty Image stock images.
Additional Credits:
  • The music is "Good Day" by DillyGotItBumpin. Check out more on Youtube!
  • Mr. West, of course, for being an inspiration.
